RogueTrader
===========

RogueTrader is a modified derivative of TradingAgents:

  https://github.com/TauricResearch/TradingAgents

The original TradingAgents project is licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0. This repository preserves the Apache License, Version 2.0 in
LICENSE.

Upstream attribution:

  TradingAgents: Multi-Agents LLM Financial Trading Framework
  Tauric Research
  https://tauric.ai/
  https://github.com/TauricResearch/TradingAgents

RogueTrader modifications include, but are not limited to:

  - Renaming and repackaging the project as RogueTrader.
  - Adding cryptocurrency-oriented analyst support, including on-chain
    analysis paths.
  - Adding DeepSeek/OpenAI-compatible provider configuration.
  - Adding local crypto data utilities and point-in-time safeguards for
    local processed data.
  - Normalizing run outputs under per-run result directories.
  - Adding structured final decision extraction.
  - Updating documentation and tests for the modified project behavior.

RogueTrader is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or maintained by Tauric
Research. TradingAgents and Tauric Research names are used only for upstream
attribution.

This project is intended for research and analysis. It is not financial,
investment, or trading advice.
